snippet.title: Shooting Gallery (Dos game 1993)
snippet.description:
Shooting Gallery has various shooting games.

1) Birds & Bottles
2) Skeet Shoot
3) Quick Draw
4) Bombs & Bells
5) Double Skeet Shoot
6) Double Quick Draw
7) Shoot Out
